.DT
set_value_info
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
set_value_info

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_value_info -  This method sets the value information for a type of special object.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_value_info(string word,
int number)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^word%^RESET%^ - the type of value information
%^BOLD%^number%^RESET%^ - the amount to set it to
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/basic/misc.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the value information for a type of
special object.  This is the extra value information associated
with the "artifact", "enchantment" or "material" of the object.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
query_value_at(), remove_value_info(), set_value()

.EP

